{"id":657039,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/【cdt发布】特朗普新冠了，中国官媒如何/","date":"2020-10-03T03:43:46Z","modified":"2020-10-04T02:46:03Z","title":"【CDT发布】特朗普新冠了，中国官媒如何反应","content":"<p>10月2日凌晨，美国总统特朗普在自己的推特上宣布，他和第一夫人的新冠病毒检测呈阳性，并启动隔离程序。消息传出后，立即上了中国社交媒体上的热搜。与中美贸易战期间相比，此时“特朗普”已经没有那么敏感。在中美贸易战最激烈的时期，特朗普为敏感词，其推特截图和带有特朗普的图片被禁止在中国社交媒体上传播。现在，特朗普似乎不再是敏感词，中国官方媒体纷纷报道了特朗普新冠检测阳性的消息，不过，却关闭了评论，或是对评论进行了精选。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657049\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/12.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"821\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/12.png 299w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/12-183x300.png 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657041\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/0.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/0.jpeg 627w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/0-277x300.jpeg 277w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657044\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"630\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/8.png 746w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/8-238x300.png 238w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657045\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"709\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/9.png 743w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/9-211x300.png 211w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/9-722x1024.png 722w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657046\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"791\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/10.png 743w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/10-190x300.png 190w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/10-648x1024.png 648w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657047\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"656\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/11.png 745w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/11-229x300.png 229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657103\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"787\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1-2.jpg 508w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1-2-191x300.jpg 191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>在疫情期间，特朗普说：没有人比我更懂病毒。再加上特朗普之前口无遮拦，什么都懂，于是中国网民封他为“懂王”。共青团中央微博放了一个有关满是“懂王”的字符，暗示特朗普新冠病毒检测阳性一事。下面的评论也在其他地方多处出现，令人怀疑这是“官方统一行动“。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657042\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"670\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1.png 743w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/1-224x300.png 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657051\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"63\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/3.png 804w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/3-300x38.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/3-768x96.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657052\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"66\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/4.png 813w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/4-300x39.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/4-768x101.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657053\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"66\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/5.png 793w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/5-300x40.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/5-768x102.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657054\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"67\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/6.png 795w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/6-300x40.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/6-768x103.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,41492,38912,38908,38923],"tags":[23028,30038,39764,13826,30630,14805]}